description: Review and practice multiplication tables from table 1 to  you decide.  Select the table you want to review or to practice.   Practice in  random order within a  given table.   Results are given with  feed back comments,  count of  questions, correct and incorrect answers. And of course you can simply ask it to multiply two numbers.  Enjoy.  Digital Spring Apps
exampleInteractions: Alexa,  open Multi Boost and multiply 3 times 3
name: Multiplication Tutor
shortDescription: A fun way to practice multiplication tables.   Review a given table or practice a table in random order.
